{"tid":1486893,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"［2018年］林鄭：警隊是對外推廣金名片","createTime":"2019-08-19T04:35:10.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-19T06:44:45.000Z","uid":149978,"like":2,"dislike":16,"uniUserReply":16,"replies":[{"pid":"82e394f46f035957eb396cc0e54a5bf731e64075","tid":1486893,"uid":149978,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-19T04:35:10.000Z","msg":"2018罪案率創新低 林鄭：警隊是對外推廣金名片<br />\n<br />\n警隊為慶祝成立175周年，舉行警民同樂日。行政長官林鄭月娥致辭時表示，警隊的文明專業令香港成為全球最安全城市，是她對外推廣的金名片。<br />\n<br />\n警隊一連兩個周末舉行175周年大會暨警民同樂日，行政長官林鄭月娥、警務處處長盧偉聰、中聯辦主任王志民在黃竹坑警察學院主持開幕禮。<br />\n<br />\n警務處長盧偉聰指2018年整體罪案數字為54,225宗，較去年下跌3.2%，是1975年以來最低。他又引述港大調查結果，指市民對多項警隊評分都創歷史新高，當中84%受訪者滿意警隊的整體表現，近八成人對警隊有信心。<br />\n<br />\n行政長官林鄭月就指，去年整體罪案數字創新低，令人鼓舞。她感謝警隊的文明專業令香港成為全球最安全城市，也是她對外推廣的金名片。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.thinkhk.com/article/2019-01/12/32320.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thinkhk.com%2Farticle%2F2019-01%2F12%2F32320.html&d=L%2B62T2%2Bn9M6BECqB4mLSsq0EM2ZTCgB2Df5M2YAuo3Y%3D&h=03992912\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.thinkhk.com/article/2019-01/12/32320.html</a>"},{"pid":"890dfc69f04df9f4a339b4b0872171160d33b54c","tid":1486893,"uid":28397,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-19T04:37:59.000Z","msg":"𠵱家變黑咭<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bb1db58f68363543b7fc934f9c5c1ae80cc2bce8","tid":1486893,"uid":40763,"like":6,"dislike":1,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-19T04:38:12.000Z","msg":"其實唔關警隊事<br />\n根本一直以來<br />\n犯得最多法既都係休班警<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"aed1103f5b7c4b72994e50e8182190c290b6ffad","tid":1486893,"uid":253826,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"rep